1) LocalBlastAnalyze.py uses local blast to analyze a list of queries with high similarity

Fist make sure you have blast+ installed.

Then check your database in folder chicken_transcripts:

blastdbcmd -list .

./chicken_genes.fa Nucleotide

Make sure that your database in blast search path:
Run this command when in chicken_transcripts folder
export BLASTDB=`pwd`

Check again by running this command from your home:

blastdbcmd -show_blastdb_search_path

Now you can use localBlastAnalalyze.py

python localBlastAnalysis.py chicken.csv chicken_genes.fa

